				"actionType": {
					"value": "passive"
				},
				"description": {
					"value": "<p>A creature @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.kWc1fhmv9LBiTuei]{Grabbed} by a canoloth lurker must attempt at a @Check[fortitude|dc:21] save.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> the creature frees themselves and is immune to Draining Tongue again for 1 day, but can still be [[/act grapple]]{Grappled} by a canoloth lurker's tongue.</p><p><strong>Success</strong> the creature takes @Damage[2d6[void]] damage and free themselves</p><p><strong>Failure</strong> the creature takes @Damage[4d6[void,persistent]] damage and is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.4D2KBtexWXa6oUMR]{Drained 1} and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.HL2l2VRSaQHu9lUw]{Fatigued}</p><p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> as failure but they're @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.4D2KBtexWXa6oUMR]{Drained 2}</p>",
